# --- Force HTTPS ---
http://gaoptimizer.com/*    https://www.gaoptimizer.com/:splat   301!
http://www.gaoptimizer.com/* https://www.gaoptimizer.com/:splat   301!

# --- Enforce Canonical Clean URLs with Trailing Slashes ---

# Redirect from the .html version to the folder version
/documentation.html   /documentation/   301!
/privacy.html         /privacy/         301!

# Redirect from the no-slash version to the folder version
/documentation        /documentation/   301!
/privacy              /privacy/         301!
/blog                 /blog/            301!